<p>Guards are the protecting force for your colony. As long as you provide a Guard with a weapon, they will protect your colony day and night.</p>

<p>There are two types of Guards: Knights and Archers. Knights use swords, while Archers use bows. (Archers don’t require arrows to shoot, unless you’ve completed the research in the <a href="../../source/buildings/university">University</a>.) You can set the type of Guard in the <a href="../../source/buildings/guardtower">Guard Tower</a> or <a href="../../source/buildings/barrackstower">Barracks Tower</a> GUI.</p>

<p>Guards will use armor when provided with some, and, if they’re a Knight, will use a shield as well (again, only if you’ve completed the research in the University).</p>
